(=^･ω･^=) 
A cat's gentle purr,  
In the night, a soft whisper,  
Mystery unfurls. ✨

What has whiskers, paws,  
And a tail that sways with grace?  
A riddle for you! 🐾

(=^･ｪ･^=)ﾉ彡☆
